      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "Version 3.3 introduces two new features!\r\n\r\n- Starfinder 2e theming!  By using `sf2e-stats` for the codeblock's language, the trait colors will switch over to Starfinder's blues.  That's the only difference at present.  If there is a larger difference between PF2e and SF2e stat block styling, please let me know.\r\n- Language overrides!  Use a heading-4 line (`#### [language code here]`) at the top of the codeblock to specify which language the stat block is being written in.  Codes for the supported languages can be found in the README.  This allows people working in multiple languages (or who are more comfortable using Obsidian in a different language than the one they play Pathfinder in) to still have accurate trait coloration.",
      "downloadCount": 351,
